Thank you very much for purchasing "Sanctuary of Promises and Contracts
~Even if Taken by Another~".

For those not interested in NTR, or those who wish to see erotic scenes
right away, you can start playing from the latter part, the heroine's
perspective "Umi's Story".

As the author, I strongly recommend playing from the beginning, but where
would you like to start playing?
